Elvira Barretto, Appellant, v. 509 Amsterdam Avenue Realty Corp., Respondent. Submitted July 9, 1964; decided July 10, 1964. *937I. Sidney Worthman for motion.

No one opposed.

Motion granted upon the ground that the determination sought to be reviewed involves a pure question of discretion of the type not reviewable by the Court of Appeals (Miranda v. City of New York, 10 N Y 2d 883).
